Section 6 — Feature Engineering

Explain engineered features.

Examples:

Total Services
Counts how many services a customer subscribes to.

Reason:

Customers using more services are more likely to stay.

CustomerValueScore
tenure × MonthlyCharges

Meaning:

Estimates customer revenue value.

ContractRiskLevel
